# No build / test runs

- Do **not** run test suites (`npm test`, `node --test`, etc.).
- Do **not** build or rebuild Docker images / Compose services, or run production/client builds (`docker compose build`, `docker compose up --build`, `npm run build`, etc.).
- The user will handle building and testing themselves.
- You may still edit test files when the task requires it, but do not execute them.
